### Estimate Browser Storage Usage

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/articles/indexeddb-max-storage-limit.html

Estimates the used storage and total allocated space for the current origin using the Storage Estimation API. This helps in understanding an application's storage footprint relative to browser limits. It returns the total quota and the current usage.

```javascript
const quota = await navigator.storage.estimate();
const totalSpace = quota.quota;
const usedSpace = quota.usage;
console.log('Approx total allocated space:', totalSpace);
console.log('Approx used space:', usedSpace);
```

