### Wrap RxStorage with Key Compression (JavaScript)

Source: https://github.com/pubkey/rxdb/blob/master/docs/key-compression.html

This snippet demonstrates how to wrap an existing RxStorage, such as the local storage plugin, with the key compression plugin. The `wrappedKeyCompressionStorage` function takes the original storage as an argument and returns a new storage instance with key compression enabled. This allows for significant disk space savings by compressing document attributes.

```javascript
import { wrappedKeyCompressionStorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/key-compression';
import { getRxStorageLocalstorage } from 'rxdb/plugins/storage-localstorage';

const storageWithKeyCompression = wrappedKeyCompressionStorage({
    storage: getRxStorageLocalstorage()
});
```

