This snippet shows the migration process when using an older RxDB version, specifically importing storage plugins from `rxdb-old`. It uses `migrateStorage` to transfer data from a database named 'myOldDatabaseName' using `getRxStorageLocalstorage` to a new database. Configuration includes batch size and parallel processing settings.

```typescript
